title: Keynsia
content:
I'd be interested to hear people's thoughts on my latest project for [Greater Albion Typefounders](http://web.archive.org/web/20150414042941/http:/gatf.wordpress.com/). It's inteneded to be a Sans Serif title face in the style of the 50s and named Keynsia after the great 'newtown' Milton Keynes.

 ![](http://web.archive.org/web/20150414042941im_/http:/typophile.com/files/Keynsia%20Test_4374.png)
